WEBVTT

00:00:29.211 --> 00:00:32.620
Love brings out an expression even parents have never seen before.

00:00:32.621 --> 00:00:34.350
It's been a while since we last greeted you.

00:00:34.351 --> 00:00:36.990
When Our Kids Fall In Love,

00:00:36.991 --> 00:00:39.120
where parents are the panel...

00:00:39.121 --> 00:00:41.760
and the children go on endless casual dates while living together,

00:00:41.761 --> 00:00:43.290
was greatly loved,

00:00:43.291 --> 00:00:45.831
and now it has returned with Season Two.

00:00:46.031 --> 00:00:48.801
(Actor Choi Jae Won)

00:00:48.901 --> 00:00:50.070
(Comedienne Lee Sung Mi)

00:00:50.071 --> 00:00:53.000
When Our Kids Fall In Love is back...

00:00:53.001 --> 00:00:54.910
for Season Two.

00:00:54.911 --> 00:00:58.540
On my right are the parents with daughters.

00:00:58.541 --> 00:00:59.740
- Hi.
- And...

00:00:59.741 --> 00:01:02.980
on the other side are the parents with sons.

00:01:02.981 --> 00:01:05.280
- I'm in your care.
- Should we greet each other?

00:01:05.281 --> 00:01:07.220
- I meant the daughters.
- After they become a couple.

00:01:07.221 --> 00:01:08.221
- I see.
- Yes.

00:01:08.321 --> 00:01:09.450
They're all remarkable people.

00:01:09.451 --> 00:01:12.061
She's the only mother...

00:01:12.621 --> 00:01:15.130
and the oldest among the parents.

00:01:15.287 --> 00:01:18.187
From what I'm seeing, the age gap...

00:01:18.587 --> 00:01:22.656
between her and Yoon Min Soo, our youngest, is 21 years.

00:01:22.657 --> 00:01:25.157
What would happen if they became in-laws?

00:01:25.297 --> 00:01:26.357
The daughter-in-law's mother?

00:01:26.757 --> 00:01:29.396
The chemistry between the parents matters too.

00:01:29.397 --> 00:01:32.367
I haven't gotten used to that hair yet.

00:01:32.567 --> 00:01:34.406
- We'll see about us.
- I see.

00:01:34.407 --> 00:01:35.966
When he went back and forth from the dressing room,

00:01:35.967 --> 00:01:38.807
I thought he was Poppin' Hyun Joon.

00:01:39.077 --> 00:01:41.176
- He and I were in a movie.
- Right.

00:01:41.177 --> 00:01:42.776
I thought it was him.

00:01:42.777 --> 00:01:46.416
You're in no place to talk about hairstyles.

00:01:46.417 --> 00:01:48.016
- Who? Him?
- You.

00:01:48.017 --> 00:01:49.147
- Me?
- Yes.

00:01:49.447 --> 00:01:51.116
I thought two old ladies came...

00:01:51.117 --> 00:01:52.787
when I saw you from behind.

00:01:54.257 --> 00:01:55.427
- Is that so?
- I see.

00:01:55.657 --> 00:01:58.926
The 1st change in Season 2 is that...

00:01:58.927 --> 00:02:03.067
someone I'm awkward with is sitting right next to me.

00:02:03.367 --> 00:02:05.066
Why are you in that seat?

00:02:05.067 --> 00:02:07.236
People loved...

00:02:07.237 --> 00:02:10.236
how I reacted and the down-to-earth comments I made last season.

00:02:10.237 --> 00:02:12.836
In Season One, Tak Soo became a couple.

00:02:12.837 --> 00:02:15.406
- Tak Soo became a final couple.
- Yes.

00:02:15.407 --> 00:02:17.016
I guess they want my good luck.

00:02:17.017 --> 00:02:18.217
(Boasting)

00:02:18.617 --> 00:02:21.486
With all due respect to everyone else here,

00:02:21.487 --> 00:02:25.056
it's been 13 years since Yoon Min Soo,

00:02:25.057 --> 00:02:28.126
Lee Jong Hyuk, and I were in...

00:02:28.127 --> 00:02:29.387
the same show and frame.

00:02:29.757 --> 00:02:32.926
We were in the same frame in 2013,

00:02:32.927 --> 00:02:37.437
and now we're in the same frame again after 13 years, as dads.

00:02:37.637 --> 00:02:40.297
I'm very happy to see them, and yet it feels strange.

00:02:40.607 --> 00:02:42.306
The fans who watched...

00:02:42.307 --> 00:02:44.036
- "Dad! Where Are We Going?" - Yes?

00:02:44.037 --> 00:02:45.306
They must have grown up too.

00:02:45.307 --> 00:02:46.677
It's their kids falling in love.

00:02:47.307 --> 00:02:50.176
The niece- and nephew-like kids they watched when they were young...

00:02:50.177 --> 00:02:51.276
- have become adults.
- Exactly.

00:02:51.277 --> 00:02:52.616
As it feels like their kids are falling in love,

00:02:52.617 --> 00:02:53.917
the show is receiving a lot of love.

00:02:53.947 --> 00:02:57.056
To think that those kids grew up and are now falling in love.

00:02:57.057 --> 00:02:58.956
I'm also filled with mixed feelings.

00:02:58.957 --> 00:03:02.256
It's our chance to discover charms...

00:03:02.257 --> 00:03:03.996
we didn't know the kids had.

00:03:03.997 --> 00:03:05.596
To me,

00:03:05.597 --> 00:03:06.956
my daughter still feels like...

00:03:06.957 --> 00:03:08.326
- a child in my arms.
- Right.

00:03:08.327 --> 00:03:10.026
But thinking that...

00:03:10.027 --> 00:03:11.096
she's at a place...

00:03:11.097 --> 00:03:13.737
- where she musters up her courage, - Yes?

00:03:13.967 --> 00:03:16.306
I'm proud of her, and she feels all grown up now.

00:03:16.307 --> 00:03:17.636
I came here...

00:03:17.637 --> 00:03:19.206
with uneasiness.

00:03:19.207 --> 00:03:21.546
I really want to know what kind of scenes we'll see.

00:03:21.547 --> 00:03:22.647
(I really want to know.)

00:03:22.877 --> 00:03:23.916
(Agreeing)

00:03:23.917 --> 00:03:25.576
- It's about to start.
- Come now.

00:03:25.577 --> 00:03:27.116
- Prepare yourselves.
- Gosh.

00:03:27.117 --> 00:03:29.086
- Here we go.
- Okay.

00:03:29.087 --> 00:03:30.586
Don't let your guards down.

00:03:30.587 --> 00:03:33.187
(The most nerve-racking moment as a parent)

00:03:33.717 --> 00:03:37.796
As a dad of a daughter, I'm both...

00:03:37.797 --> 00:03:39.797
- excited and worried.
- I know, right?

00:03:40.027 --> 00:03:43.227
Gosh, why am I getting so nervous over this?

00:03:44.567 --> 00:03:47.606
(What will it be like to watch...)

00:03:47.607 --> 00:03:52.637
(my kid fall in love for the first time?)

00:03:56.907 --> 00:04:00.047
(Pyeongchang, Gangwon Province)

00:04:01.547 --> 00:04:04.186
(Christmas, December 25, 2025)

00:04:04.187 --> 00:04:06.487
- It's Christmas.
- Look at that nice atmosphere.

00:04:07.387 --> 00:04:12.957
(How will it feel to watch my all-grown-up kid in love?)

00:04:13.297 --> 00:04:15.397
There he is. That's Hoo.

00:04:16.727 --> 00:04:17.767
My son.

00:04:19.667 --> 00:04:21.566
How adorable.

00:04:21.567 --> 00:04:23.667
That's a familiar photo.

00:04:26.107 --> 00:04:27.247
Cute.

00:04:30.547 --> 00:04:32.517
- That's Moon Sik's son.
- Right?

00:04:33.277 --> 00:04:34.517
Wait, that's my daughter.

00:04:36.817 --> 00:04:42.357
(Episode 1: Romantic Holiday)

00:04:47.597 --> 00:04:53.667
(The first son is wearing a long coat.)

00:04:55.537 --> 00:04:56.636
- Who is it?
- It's a guy.

00:04:56.637 --> 00:04:57.637
He's wearing a coat.

00:04:58.977 --> 00:05:00.037
Isn't it Chow Yun Fat?

00:05:08.717 --> 00:05:11.156
- Here comes the first son.
- Here he enters.

00:05:11.157 --> 00:05:16.057
(Whose son is he?)

00:05:27.537 --> 00:05:29.406
(The parents with daughters recognize him right away.)

00:05:29.407 --> 00:05:31.236
- He's grown into a fine man.
- Yoon Hoo.

00:05:31.237 --> 00:05:32.536
He used to get jjajang ramyeon...

00:05:32.537 --> 00:05:33.836
- all over his face.
- Right?

00:05:33.837 --> 00:05:35.806
That kid was a total crybaby.

00:05:35.807 --> 00:05:38.517
- To think I'd see Hoo like this.
- Gosh.

00:05:38.617 --> 00:05:39.676
What a looker.

00:05:39.677 --> 00:05:41.587
(My son is a looker!)

00:05:42.747 --> 00:05:46.486
(The only son who was a cutie pie)

00:05:46.487 --> 00:05:47.957
That's so cute.

00:05:48.727 --> 00:05:50.697
(The national nephew joined at the hip with his dad)

00:05:51.697 --> 00:05:54.367
(Growing up in the blink of an eye)

00:05:54.827 --> 00:05:56.396
(Before we knew it, Yoon Hoo is now an adult.)

00:05:56.397 --> 00:05:57.897
What a cool photo.

00:05:58.937 --> 00:06:00.036
Hi.

00:06:00.037 --> 00:06:03.307
As a sophomore majoring in business...

00:06:03.837 --> 00:06:06.007
at the University of North Carolina, I'm Yoon Hoo.

00:06:07.307 --> 00:06:09.406
- He's majoring in business?
- A business major?

00:06:09.407 --> 00:06:10.446
(The dads with daughters are interested.)

00:06:10.447 --> 00:06:13.176
- He brought honor to the family.
- He grew up well.

00:06:13.177 --> 00:06:15.647
- I know, right?
- Goodness.

00:06:16.117 --> 00:06:18.286
While living in the US,

00:06:18.287 --> 00:06:21.587
I've been into working out these days.

00:06:22.457 --> 00:06:24.826
About six times a week.

00:06:24.827 --> 00:06:26.296
- Six times?
- Two to two and a half hours...

00:06:26.297 --> 00:06:27.767
each time.

00:06:34.907 --> 00:06:40.277
(His muscular body is giving off manliness.)

00:06:41.207 --> 00:06:42.577
(Oh, my.)

00:06:42.877 --> 00:06:44.177
Do you like it, ma'am?

00:06:44.517 --> 00:06:45.577
Yes.

00:06:47.317 --> 00:06:48.717
That's the kind of son I raised.

00:06:49.087 --> 00:06:50.586
(The parents with daughters are satisfied.)

00:06:50.587 --> 00:06:52.017
My gosh.

00:06:52.257 --> 00:06:54.927
It's hard to pick the part I'm most confident in,

00:06:55.187 --> 00:06:56.227
but I guess it's my shoulders.

00:06:59.057 --> 00:07:00.797
Did he have to make that face?

00:07:02.597 --> 00:07:04.437
Thanks to my dad's genes,

00:07:04.567 --> 00:07:06.266
my rear delts look quite fine.

00:07:06.267 --> 00:07:08.136
- That's why my shoulders are round.
- My family...

00:07:08.137 --> 00:07:10.367
- has broad shoulders.
- Really? I see.

00:07:11.107 --> 00:07:12.107
(Any dating experience?)

00:07:12.108 --> 00:07:13.206
I've dated...

00:07:13.207 --> 00:07:15.407
once in high school and then once in college.

00:07:16.447 --> 00:07:17.776
So he had girlfriends.

00:07:17.777 --> 00:07:18.817
(To think Hoo dated!)

00:07:18.947 --> 00:07:21.347
My parents have no idea.

00:07:22.087 --> 00:07:23.487
- I don't tell them about it.
- I really don't.

00:07:23.917 --> 00:07:25.187
I don't want to tell them.

00:07:25.757 --> 00:07:27.387
My parents are like,

00:07:27.727 --> 00:07:29.087
"Is she pretty?"

00:07:29.227 --> 00:07:30.526
"Show me a photo of her."

00:07:30.527 --> 00:07:31.957
Especially my dad.

00:07:32.427 --> 00:07:34.167
"What's her major?"

00:07:34.397 --> 00:07:36.897
"I can tell just by looking at her face."

00:07:37.197 --> 00:07:38.367
(Embarrassed)

00:07:38.437 --> 00:07:40.396
I would do the same if I were him.

00:07:40.397 --> 00:07:42.606
It's one of the many phrases Yoon Min Soo often uses.

00:07:42.607 --> 00:07:43.937
- "I can tell." - I can tell.

00:07:44.807 --> 00:07:46.737
(What do you think your charm is?)

00:07:47.037 --> 00:07:49.847
Just like when I was young, I'm sweet.

00:07:51.147 --> 00:07:52.917
My personality changing while growing up...

00:07:54.187 --> 00:07:56.047
I'm a tough guy.

00:07:56.447 --> 00:07:58.017
"Flirting" is the word, right?

00:07:58.217 --> 00:07:59.417
I think I'll be good at it.

00:08:00.787 --> 00:08:02.057
When I had feelings,

00:08:02.757 --> 00:08:04.397
I'd even promise her the moon and the stars.

00:08:05.827 --> 00:08:07.767
How did I do that? By pinky promising.

00:08:13.397 --> 00:08:14.437
Are you kidding me?

00:08:14.837 --> 00:08:17.167
- He's got the right attitude.
- Totally.

00:08:17.777 --> 00:08:20.206
- He has the face of a baby...
- Yes?

00:08:20.207 --> 00:08:22.806
But talks like...

00:08:22.807 --> 00:08:24.777
- A tough guy.
- someone our age.

00:08:25.877 --> 00:08:27.316
- He's quite mature.
- Yes, mature.

00:08:27.317 --> 00:08:28.916
- He's mature.
- So he's mature.

00:08:28.917 --> 00:08:30.087
You're right.

00:08:30.717 --> 00:08:36.057
(Yoon Hoo, a self-proclaimed tough guy)

00:08:38.027 --> 00:08:41.997
(1st-floor living room)

00:08:47.567 --> 00:08:50.407
(Extremely nervous)

00:08:56.077 --> 00:08:58.017
(Glancing)

00:09:05.387 --> 00:09:09.787
(Yoon Hoo starts looking around.)

00:09:11.827 --> 00:09:13.357
(Standing up)

00:09:16.767 --> 00:09:19.267
(Peeking)

00:09:23.637 --> 00:09:25.007
- What is it?
- What?

00:09:25.707 --> 00:09:26.707
What's wrong?

00:09:28.407 --> 00:09:29.847
He must be looking around.

00:09:34.517 --> 00:09:35.787
I need to use the bathroom.

00:09:36.787 --> 00:09:37.816
The bathroom?

00:09:37.817 --> 00:09:39.917
(To use the bathroom as soon as you arrive?)

00:09:40.717 --> 00:09:43.127
(The next resident will arrive soon.)

00:09:44.297 --> 00:09:46.957
(A worrisome start)

00:09:48.927 --> 00:09:50.027
I don't care.

00:09:56.137 --> 00:09:57.237
I found it.

00:09:58.807 --> 00:10:00.236
He should make a cool first impression,

00:10:00.237 --> 00:10:01.276
but he's using the bathroom.

00:10:01.277 --> 00:10:02.577
- Right?
- Yoon Hoo is...

00:10:03.077 --> 00:10:05.076
Has anyone ever appeared first...

00:10:05.077 --> 00:10:08.446
and then gone straight to the bathroom on a dating show?

00:10:08.447 --> 00:10:10.186
- He's the first.
- The first.

00:10:10.187 --> 00:10:11.356
(The very first guy to go straight to the bathroom)

00:10:11.357 --> 00:10:12.357
(Munching)

00:10:12.358 --> 00:10:13.557
What is he doing?

00:10:14.887 --> 00:10:16.387
Yoon Min Soo has started snacking.

00:10:16.927 --> 00:10:19.057
He's no testosterone man.

00:10:19.227 --> 00:10:20.357
Just look at him.

00:10:21.097 --> 00:10:22.527
Yoon Min Soo is running low on sugar.

00:10:24.497 --> 00:10:28.837
(While the first resident has left, )

00:10:30.137 --> 00:10:35.077
(the second resident approaches.)

00:10:36.047 --> 00:10:37.577
It's a girl.

00:10:38.217 --> 00:10:39.477
- A girl.
- Who is she?

00:10:39.617 --> 00:10:41.847
- How pretty.
- She's already pretty.

00:10:42.687 --> 00:10:43.816
Whose daughter is she?

00:10:43.817 --> 00:10:44.957
(The dads of sons stare at the screen.)

00:10:47.487 --> 00:10:49.487
- She's slim.
- My gosh.

00:10:50.287 --> 00:10:51.326
Cool.

00:10:51.327 --> 00:10:53.857
(Excited)

00:10:58.397 --> 00:11:03.367
(Nervous)

00:11:03.737 --> 00:11:06.136
One parent is glued to the screen.

00:11:06.137 --> 00:11:07.576
- I wonder whose daughter she is.
- He's ready...

00:11:07.577 --> 00:11:09.547
- to jump into the TV.
- I know, right?

00:11:11.377 --> 00:11:12.517
Who could it be?

00:11:24.357 --> 00:11:26.596
(Wide-eyed)

00:11:26.597 --> 00:11:27.667
For real?

00:11:28.727 --> 00:11:31.197
Hi, I'm Park Si Woo.

00:11:32.297 --> 00:11:33.896
- Are we correct?
- It's his daughter.

00:11:33.897 --> 00:11:35.537
- Is she your daughter?
- They look alike.

00:11:35.637 --> 00:11:37.536
- How pretty.
- Seriously?

00:11:37.537 --> 00:11:40.037
- My gosh.
- You really won in life.

00:11:46.747 --> 00:11:49.987
(The precious second daughter who was glued to her dad)

00:11:50.647 --> 00:11:53.317
- Oh, my.
- That's a recent photo.

00:11:53.817 --> 00:11:57.827
I always feel the need to do my best,

00:11:58.427 --> 00:12:00.727
so I hate wasting time.

00:12:02.227 --> 00:12:03.767
She's really cute.

00:12:04.337 --> 00:12:06.637
Studying Japanese or English.

00:12:07.467 --> 00:12:09.637
Running 10km every day.

00:12:10.367 --> 00:12:12.107
With my packed schedule,

00:12:13.107 --> 00:12:14.877
I had no time to date.

00:12:15.507 --> 00:12:17.576
- Every day?
- She's big on self-management.

00:12:17.577 --> 00:12:19.347
Park Nam Jung's second daughter...

00:12:19.817 --> 00:12:21.416
is pretty and even smart.

00:12:21.417 --> 00:12:23.017
- Is that so?
- And...

00:12:23.187 --> 00:12:25.887
I heard Si Woo got five admissions offers.

00:12:26.257 --> 00:12:29.126
She got accepted into five colleges at the same time.

00:12:29.127 --> 00:12:30.426
(Growing anxiety)

00:12:30.427 --> 00:12:31.656
When she applied to them?

00:12:31.657 --> 00:12:32.826
Just before this show,

00:12:32.827 --> 00:12:35.397
she passed the Japanese proficiency exam.

00:12:35.927 --> 00:12:38.166
- In that short time?
- I had no idea she was studying.

00:12:38.167 --> 00:12:40.837
She prepared in her room for 1 to 2 months.

00:12:41.167 --> 00:12:42.267
Do you have my phone?

00:12:42.707 --> 00:12:45.136
I should have Min Kuk join as the latecomer.

00:12:45.137 --> 00:12:46.337
- Really?
- Yes.

00:12:46.707 --> 00:12:49.246
- She already has what it takes.
- You're right.

00:12:49.247 --> 00:12:51.647
And she's the first daughter.

00:12:51.717 --> 00:12:53.117
If this is how amazing the first is...

00:12:53.317 --> 00:12:55.386
- She hates wasting time.
- Exactly.

00:12:55.387 --> 00:12:56.387
What a bright girl.

00:12:56.388 --> 00:12:57.787
I feel bad for my daughter.

00:13:01.457 --> 00:13:03.987
When people meet me for the first time,

00:13:04.327 --> 00:13:07.256
many say I look cold...

00:13:07.257 --> 00:13:09.597
and hard to approach.

00:13:09.727 --> 00:13:12.137
When I'm in front of my crush,

00:13:12.467 --> 00:13:15.867
I become extremely awkward.

00:13:17.007 --> 00:13:18.407
"I want a boyfriend."

00:13:18.537 --> 00:13:20.007
It's always on my mind.

00:13:20.407 --> 00:13:23.677
But things don't go the way you want them to.

00:13:24.547 --> 00:13:26.917
It'd be awesome if I found someone I really click with...

00:13:27.987 --> 00:13:30.517
and who makes my heart flutter.

00:13:32.317 --> 00:13:38.127
(Park Si Woo, an alpha girl in everything but dating)

00:13:38.897 --> 00:13:39.897
(The living room is empty.)

00:13:39.898 --> 00:13:41.397
Can I sit anywhere?

00:13:47.807 --> 00:13:49.606
(Yoon Hoo is still in the bathroom.)

00:13:49.607 --> 00:13:51.976
- What is Hoo doing?
- What is he doing?

00:13:51.977 --> 00:13:53.137
What's taking so long?

00:13:58.177 --> 00:14:04.087
(Not knowing about it, Si Woo keeps waiting.)

00:14:05.357 --> 00:14:06.417
Oh, no.

00:14:06.557 --> 00:14:08.587
(The only person who can't laugh)

00:14:09.687 --> 00:14:10.887
Is Hoo pooping?

00:14:12.497 --> 00:14:14.227
He could've gone to check himself out in the mirror.

00:14:14.627 --> 00:14:16.727
(If only that were true.)

00:14:17.697 --> 00:14:23.137
(Why were you in the bathroom for so long?)

00:14:24.777 --> 00:14:26.207
I got nervous.

00:14:26.777 --> 00:14:28.547
I took a dump. I did.

00:14:28.707 --> 00:14:29.907
Hoo pooped.

00:14:30.847 --> 00:14:32.477
- That's not easy.
- He pooped.

00:14:33.247 --> 00:14:34.547
