00:53:18.137 --> 00:53:21.777
and apologizing afterward.

00:53:22.237 --> 00:53:23.506
- About five minutes?
- Five minutes?

00:53:23.507 --> 00:53:24.876
I didn't wait for too long.

00:53:24.877 --> 00:53:26.576
(Apologizing)

00:53:26.577 --> 00:53:27.577
Am I wrong?

00:53:27.578 --> 00:53:29.147
(Apologizing for the 2nd time)

00:53:29.317 --> 00:53:31.287
(Apologizing for the 3rd time)

00:53:31.517 --> 00:53:33.017
(Why do you keep apologizing?)

00:53:33.287 --> 00:53:34.486
"Why do you keep apologizing?"

00:53:34.487 --> 00:53:35.786
He flirted by being nice.

00:53:35.787 --> 00:53:37.687
- He flirted by being nice?
- Yes.

00:53:38.387 --> 00:53:40.057
I received two votes.

00:53:40.427 --> 00:53:42.627
Of course, I was excited. I was excited.

00:53:42.997 --> 00:53:45.296
The fact that I received 2 out of 3 votes...

00:53:45.297 --> 00:53:46.727
It's... What do you call it?

00:53:49.337 --> 00:53:51.337
It's something any male would be thankful for.

00:53:52.667 --> 00:53:54.237
- "Any male?" - "Any male?"

00:53:54.637 --> 00:53:56.036
Why does he use such strange words?

00:53:56.037 --> 00:53:58.307
We have the results of the First Impression Selection.

00:53:58.547 --> 00:54:00.476
Min Soo and Nam Jung...

00:54:00.477 --> 00:54:02.446
must be happy. How does it feel?

00:54:02.447 --> 00:54:04.147
While I'm happy,

00:54:04.347 --> 00:54:06.386
the fact that she wasn't matched with her pick...

00:54:06.387 --> 00:54:08.316
(Si Woo and Hoo didn't choose each other.)

00:54:08.317 --> 00:54:11.156
I'll need to wait and see. Yes.

00:54:11.157 --> 00:54:12.627
- It was just the first impression.
- That's right.

00:54:13.757 --> 00:54:17.696
(The First Impression Selection has ended.)

00:54:17.697 --> 00:54:20.337
I didn't get chosen by anyone.

00:54:24.167 --> 00:54:26.066
I didn't have high hopes.

00:54:26.067 --> 00:54:28.976
Because I'm very quiet...

00:54:28.977 --> 00:54:30.476
(She has a quiet personality.)

00:54:30.477 --> 00:54:34.047
It would've been hard for them to choose me.

00:54:35.177 --> 00:54:38.187
"From now on, I'll make more effort..."

00:54:38.687 --> 00:54:41.217
"and converse with them."

00:54:41.487 --> 00:54:43.787
- I had that thought.
- That's a great attitude.

00:54:43.957 --> 00:54:45.626
That's right. Don't give up.

00:54:45.627 --> 00:54:46.926
I agree. Don't give up.

00:54:46.927 --> 00:54:48.857
That's right. She needs to keep going until the end.

00:54:49.097 --> 00:54:50.166
That's right.

00:54:50.167 --> 00:54:52.567
(Another person who didn't get any votes)

00:54:52.767 --> 00:54:55.366
- Shin Jae Hyuk!
- Why didn't he get any votes?

00:54:55.367 --> 00:54:56.397
(Shin Jae Hyuk!)

00:54:56.737 --> 00:54:58.737
I thought, "It's understandable."

00:54:59.707 --> 00:55:01.306
It hadn't been long since I had entered.

00:55:01.307 --> 00:55:03.706
(Jae Hyuk entered last.)

00:55:03.707 --> 00:55:06.247
"They haven't seen much of me."

00:55:06.407 --> 00:55:07.516
I had that thought.

00:55:07.517 --> 00:55:08.517
- Of course.
- That's right.

00:55:08.518 --> 00:55:09.946
Of course. This is the beginning.

00:55:09.947 --> 00:55:11.447
It was just a warmup, my son.

00:55:13.117 --> 00:55:14.317
I'll seize victory.

00:55:15.117 --> 00:55:16.617
I like taking the difficult path.

00:55:18.157 --> 00:55:20.087
That's right. He can turn the tables.

00:55:23.567 --> 00:55:26.297
Now, shall we move?

00:55:27.167 --> 00:55:28.766
Move? To where?

00:55:28.767 --> 00:55:30.707
- Let's tour the room.
- I see. Let's do that.

00:55:31.207 --> 00:55:32.667
"Let's tour the room." Nice use of English.

00:55:32.907 --> 00:55:34.036
Nice use of English.

00:55:34.037 --> 00:55:36.377
Why are you making a big deal out of nothing?

00:55:38.047 --> 00:55:39.376
(We introduce the lodging the kids will stay at.)

00:55:39.377 --> 00:55:41.917
We can go here first.

00:55:43.277 --> 00:55:45.316
(There are two doors by the entrance.)

00:55:45.317 --> 00:55:46.347
I was curious.

00:55:47.517 --> 00:55:48.586
It's a room.

00:55:48.587 --> 00:55:49.686
(Women's room by the entrance)

00:55:49.687 --> 00:55:51.327
- It's pretty.
- It's pretty.

00:55:52.187 --> 00:55:54.296
(Men's room on the opposite side)

00:55:54.297 --> 00:55:56.196
I'll be happy every day if I live in a house like this.

00:55:56.197 --> 00:55:57.227
Right.

00:55:58.267 --> 00:56:01.037
(They cross the living room to the opposite side.)

00:56:03.067 --> 00:56:04.206
- Shall we go upstairs?
- Shall we go upstairs?

00:56:04.207 --> 00:56:05.207
That sounds good.

00:56:06.607 --> 00:56:08.407
Is it the Photo Room?

00:56:09.307 --> 00:56:12.077
- It's the Photo Room.
- There is the Photo Room.

00:56:13.377 --> 00:56:15.076
- Yes. It's the Photo Room.
- What's that?

00:56:15.077 --> 00:56:16.986
- Photo Room.
- It has been decorated well.

00:56:16.987 --> 00:56:18.616
Season One didn't have this room.

00:56:18.617 --> 00:56:19.617
That's right.

00:56:19.618 --> 00:56:21.417
These must be our old photos.

00:56:22.117 --> 00:56:23.157
Hold on a second.

00:56:23.787 --> 00:56:24.927
Gosh, it's me!

00:56:26.257 --> 00:56:28.226
There are the kids' old photos.

00:56:28.227 --> 00:56:29.626
(Over the past memories, )

00:56:29.627 --> 00:56:30.996
It'll be fun to study them.

00:56:30.997 --> 00:56:32.266
That's right.

00:56:32.267 --> 00:56:34.897
(they'll make new memories.)

00:56:36.237 --> 00:56:38.566
Let's go up one more floor.

00:56:38.567 --> 00:56:40.307
(They go up one more floor.)

00:56:41.037 --> 00:56:42.776
(What is this place with the antique interior for?)

00:56:42.777 --> 00:56:43.877
My goodness.

00:56:45.007 --> 00:56:46.007
This is incredible.

00:56:46.907 --> 00:56:47.916
(Letter Room)

00:56:47.917 --> 00:56:50.016
- What's this place?
- It's the Letter Room.

00:56:50.017 --> 00:56:51.047
Letter Room.

00:56:52.747 --> 00:56:54.187
Shall we read this?

00:56:55.887 --> 00:56:57.257
"The Letter Room guide."

00:56:57.487 --> 00:57:00.227
"This is the Letter Room you can use anytime."

00:57:01.257 --> 00:57:02.926
"Write down what you want to say..."

00:57:02.927 --> 00:57:04.667
"and put it inside the recipient's mailbox."

00:57:05.327 --> 00:57:07.437
"The letter will be delivered to that person."

00:57:09.197 --> 00:57:10.806
That must be where you write love letters.

00:57:10.807 --> 00:57:12.267
A hand-written letter.

00:57:12.537 --> 00:57:14.036
None of them would've written a letter before.

00:57:14.037 --> 00:57:15.137
Right.

00:57:16.407 --> 00:57:18.007
Are these ours?

00:57:19.547 --> 00:57:20.646
My gosh.

00:57:20.647 --> 00:57:23.077
(The mailboxes where their feelings will be delivered)

00:57:24.417 --> 00:57:27.657
Having your own mailbox...

00:57:28.317 --> 00:57:30.157
made me feel nervous.

00:57:30.357 --> 00:57:33.827
If I were to receive a letter, I'd actually feel fluttered.

00:57:34.727 --> 00:57:37.027
If I like someone,

00:57:37.097 --> 00:57:38.727
I'll practice my handwriting...

00:57:39.027 --> 00:57:41.867
and write a letter.

00:57:48.307 --> 00:57:50.947
(The place where you write how you feel...)

00:57:51.647 --> 00:57:56.477
(and read those feelings)

00:57:56.777 --> 00:57:58.487
- It's so sentimental.
- Yes.

00:57:58.687 --> 00:58:00.657
When you write a letter, you get to think about that person,

00:58:00.817 --> 00:58:02.656
and you need to put your effort into each letter.

00:58:02.657 --> 00:58:04.326
- They will write carefully.
- Carefully.

00:58:04.327 --> 00:58:06.457
That would become the strongest way to flirt.

00:58:07.027 --> 00:58:09.727
I have a feeling a lot of history would be written here.

00:58:11.727 --> 00:58:13.196
(Where their true feelings are recorded)

00:58:13.197 --> 00:58:18.737
(What sincere emotions will be written?)

00:58:19.767 --> 00:58:21.776
How should we decide the room? How would you like it?

00:58:21.777 --> 00:58:23.707
- I don't mind anything.
- I don't mind either.

00:58:24.247 --> 00:58:25.846
(Cho Eun Byul and Park Si Woo)

00:58:25.847 --> 00:58:28.447
They have so many cute stickers.

00:58:28.847 --> 00:58:29.916
Thank you.

00:58:29.917 --> 00:58:31.416
Where... Should I put it inside?

00:58:31.417 --> 00:58:32.887
- Yes, please.
- Someone is at Yu Bin's room.

00:58:33.817 --> 00:58:35.157
- Goodness.
- It's Yoon Hoo.

00:58:35.187 --> 00:58:36.686
- Yoon Hoo...
- It's Yoon Hoo.

00:58:36.687 --> 00:58:38.356
(Yoon Hoo carries Yu Bin's luggage to her room.)

00:58:38.357 --> 00:58:39.557
- Here, yes.
- Here?

00:58:39.927 --> 00:58:41.526
- He sure is well-mannered.
- Nice.

00:58:41.527 --> 00:58:44.297
- I wonder if he knows how it feels.
- I wonder.

00:58:44.667 --> 00:58:46.696
I wonder if he does or not.

00:58:46.697 --> 00:58:48.667
(Satisfied)

00:58:49.367 --> 00:58:53.607
(Lee Jae Seung, the men's room beside the stairs)

00:58:54.907 --> 00:58:56.636
- This isn't easy.
- I know, right?

00:58:56.637 --> 00:58:59.007
(Shin Jae Hyuk and Yoon Hoo, the men's room beside the entrance)

00:59:00.617 --> 00:59:02.847
(Knocking)

00:59:02.947 --> 00:59:04.416
I have nothing to do.

00:59:04.417 --> 00:59:05.887
We also...

00:59:06.287 --> 00:59:08.586
Did you unpack or...

00:59:08.587 --> 00:59:09.916
(Ding dong)

00:59:09.917 --> 00:59:11.286
- That...
- How...

00:59:11.287 --> 00:59:12.357
(Startled)

00:59:12.957 --> 00:59:13.957
Someone's coming.

00:59:14.357 --> 00:59:16.027
- A parcel?
- Who would join already?

00:59:16.357 --> 00:59:17.626
Is the latecomer already here?

00:59:17.627 --> 00:59:20.497
- No way.
- They wouldn't join so fast.

00:59:20.837 --> 00:59:22.497
- Joon Soo would definitely come.
- This...

00:59:23.837 --> 00:59:26.536
There must be a reason you're here.

00:59:26.537 --> 00:59:27.806
That's true.

00:59:27.807 --> 00:59:29.537
It's game over once Joon Soo joins.

00:59:32.307 --> 00:59:33.646
What... Goodness.

00:59:33.647 --> 00:59:35.346
(Who rang the bell?)

00:59:35.347 --> 00:59:36.647
Something's here.

00:59:42.157 --> 00:59:43.686
What's this?

00:59:43.687 --> 00:59:46.087
- Gosh, what's this?
- Christmas presents?

00:59:46.487 --> 00:59:48.757
- Goodness.
- It's Christmas today.

00:59:48.857 --> 00:59:50.056
Presents?

00:59:50.057 --> 00:59:51.366
It's already Christmas.

00:59:51.367 --> 00:59:52.596
Could Joon Soo be in there?

00:59:52.597 --> 00:59:53.936
Will Joon Soo appear from there?

00:59:53.937 --> 00:59:56.167
He could appear like this.

00:59:56.597 --> 00:59:57.806
It must be tough in there, Joon Soo.

00:59:57.807 --> 00:59:59.506
- That's possible.
- He's so tall too.

00:59:59.507 --> 01:00:01.276
- Ta-da.
- He's tall.

01:00:01.277 --> 01:00:02.407
(They keep being suspicious of Joon Soo making an appearance.)

01:00:03.377 --> 01:00:05.207
- Can you carry it yourself?
- Let me help.

01:00:05.407 --> 01:00:06.477
I'll hold the top.

01:00:08.917 --> 01:00:10.487
She's strong.

01:00:11.187 --> 01:00:12.686
- Here.
- Yu Bin is strong.

01:00:12.687 --> 01:00:14.656
She's strong.

01:00:14.657 --> 01:00:15.917
Yes.

01:00:16.017 --> 01:00:18.026
Why isn't Jae Seung helping out?

01:00:18.027 --> 01:00:21.297
(He can only laugh.)

01:00:22.157 --> 01:00:23.196
We got a letter.

01:00:23.197 --> 01:00:25.327
(And a letter arrived too.)

01:00:27.297 --> 01:00:29.797
"Split up into teams and perform these tasks."

01:00:30.467 --> 01:00:32.707
"Cooking and decorating Christmas trees."

01:00:33.467 --> 01:00:34.876
It's not a 2-on-2.

01:00:34.877 --> 01:00:37.077
(3-on-3 mini date)

01:00:37.277 --> 01:00:39.676
It could be 2 men and 1 woman...

01:00:39.677 --> 01:00:41.346
- or 2 women and 1 man.
- That's right.

01:00:41.347 --> 01:00:43.146
- They'll be mixed.
- Exactly.

01:00:43.147 --> 01:00:46.346
They can spend time with those they're interested in...

01:00:46.347 --> 01:00:48.156
- That's it.
- and appeal to them naturally.

01:00:48.157 --> 01:00:49.456
- That's right.
- It's a good opportunity.

01:00:49.457 --> 01:00:50.886
It's game over then.

01:00:50.887 --> 01:00:52.386
(Looking forward to it)

01:00:52.387 --> 01:00:54.927
- Three on each team.
- Two tasks?

01:00:55.257 --> 01:00:56.257
Three on each team.

01:00:57.927 --> 01:01:00.497
We're finally starting.

01:01:00.667 --> 01:01:03.636
I wanted to be on the same team as Yoon Hoo.

01:01:03.637 --> 01:01:05.136
My gosh.

01:01:05.137 --> 01:01:06.207
Good.

01:01:08.107 --> 01:01:09.177
Yoon Hoo.

01:01:09.677 --> 01:01:12.347
- I wanted to work with him.
- Of course you'd want that.

01:01:12.907 --> 01:01:14.046
Yoon Hoo is popular.

01:01:14.047 --> 01:01:15.777
Hoo is very popular.

01:01:18.417 --> 01:01:21.457
I want to be on the same team as Si Woo.

01:01:30.827 --> 01:01:33.527
- Are they reading the room?
- They can't take the initiative.

01:01:35.967 --> 01:01:38.337
I heard you liked cooking.

01:01:39.067 --> 01:01:40.207
I see.

01:01:41.577 --> 01:01:42.577
Meat...

01:01:42.577 --> 01:01:43.577
(You said you were good at cooking meat.)

01:01:43.607 --> 01:01:45.306
Meat?

01:01:45.307 --> 01:01:46.447
(Yoon Hoo ends up in the cooking team.)

01:01:47.077 --> 01:01:49.046
- Meat?
- Meat? I'll make pasta.

01:01:49.047 --> 01:01:50.346
Pasta?

01:01:50.347 --> 01:01:51.717
- She joined immediately.
- She said pasta.

01:01:52.047 --> 01:01:54.186
- Pasta?
- She joins him by saying pasta.

01:01:54.187 --> 01:01:56.116
(Cooking team, Yoon Hoo, Choi Yu Bin)

01:01:56.117 --> 01:01:57.157
Cooking?

01:01:57.987 --> 01:01:59.327
I'll cook eggs.

01:01:59.687 --> 01:02:01.326
She joined the cooking team.

01:02:01.327 --> 01:02:02.427
This is how...

01:02:03.127 --> 01:02:05.026
- Meat?
- Meat? I'll make pasta.

01:02:05.027 --> 01:02:09.667
(The cooking team is formed quickly around Yoon Hoo.)

01:02:09.937 --> 01:02:12.936
- My gosh.
- They're quick thinkers.

01:02:12.937 --> 01:02:14.176
(The dads are taken back by their daughters' speed.)

01:02:14.177 --> 01:02:17.507
As soon as Yoon Hoo made up his mind, two people followed.

01:02:18.177 --> 01:02:19.346
(He spots something.)

01:02:19.347 --> 01:02:22.076
Min Soo is sitting arrogantly.

01:02:22.077 --> 01:02:23.176
Look at his posture.

01:02:23.177 --> 01:02:24.446
Let me have some snacks.

01:02:24.447 --> 01:02:25.486
(His confidence is boosted thanks to his son.)

01:02:25.487 --> 01:02:27.456
He is finally...

01:02:27.457 --> 01:02:28.716
Before we started,

01:02:28.717 --> 01:02:30.727
we said we could hold each other by the collar.

01:02:31.287 --> 01:02:33.026
I'm quite worried about this.

01:02:33.027 --> 01:02:34.126
(Si Woo's dad suddenly gets angry at his cocky attitude.)

01:02:34.127 --> 01:02:36.126
He scored too many from the start.

01:02:36.127 --> 01:02:37.627
(For how long will he keep his smile?)

01:02:38.997 --> 01:02:43.537
(How did you feel when you became the same team as Yu Bin and Si Woo?)

01:02:45.537 --> 01:02:49.607
I coincidentally became the same team...

01:02:49.777 --> 01:02:53.446
with the two people I was most curious about.

01:02:53.447 --> 01:02:56.747
I wanted to use this chance to get to know them well.

01:02:57.617 --> 01:03:00.687
Yoon Hoo is interested in Si Woo too.

01:03:02.517 --> 01:03:04.686
- Then the three of us...
- The tree?

01:03:04.687 --> 01:03:05.726
- The tree.
- Are you okay with it?

01:03:05.727 --> 01:03:07.026
- Are you okay with it?
- Yes.

01:03:07.027 --> 01:03:08.157
(Jae Seung, Jae Hyuk, and Eun Byul became Team Tree.)

01:03:09.197 --> 01:03:10.597
It was a shame,

01:03:10.827 --> 01:03:12.527
but I still have a lot of time.

01:03:13.127 --> 01:03:15.197
Jae Hyuk isn't assertive.

01:03:17.067 --> 01:03:19.866
I got on the same team as the person...

01:03:19.867 --> 01:03:21.206
I chose for the first impression.

01:03:21.207 --> 01:03:23.607
I got the chance to talk with him.

01:03:24.007 --> 01:03:25.177
- So I was really happy.
- My gosh.

01:03:25.777 --> 01:03:28.147
- It's a chance for Eun Byul.
- That's right.

01:03:29.717 --> 01:03:31.216
Shall we get started?

01:03:31.217 --> 01:03:32.287
- Okay.
- Let's do it.

01:03:33.987 --> 01:03:35.287
How does kimchi fried rice sound?

01:03:35.617 --> 01:03:37.426
- I'm fine with anything.
- Really?

01:03:37.427 --> 01:03:38.487
I'll eat anything happily.

01:03:40.957 --> 01:03:42.227
Do you like eggs?

01:03:42.557 --> 01:03:43.627
Eggs?

01:03:44.067 --> 01:03:45.466
Eggs are a must for kimchi fried rice.

01:03:45.467 --> 01:03:46.827
Okay. Then...

01:03:46.997 --> 01:03:48.266
- shall I make fried eggs?
- Fried eggs?

01:03:48.267 --> 01:03:49.636
- Fried eggs?
- Sounds good.

01:03:49.637 --> 01:03:51.036
- Six?
- Sure.

01:03:51.037 --> 01:03:52.037
(Today's main menu with Assistant Si Woo)

01:03:52.038 --> 01:03:54.636
- Then...
- Kimchi fried rice and steak.

01:03:54.637 --> 01:03:55.937
(Yu Bin's kimchi fried rice and Yoon Hoo's steak)

01:03:56.477 --> 01:03:58.847
Yoon Hoo must be careful with his actions here.

01:03:59.047 --> 01:04:00.047
- Yes.
- That's right.

01:04:00.048 --> 01:04:01.316
- Depending on...
- Exactly.

01:04:01.317 --> 01:04:02.376
- who he talks more to, - Yes.

01:04:02.377 --> 01:04:04.617
- one of them could feel hurt.
- That's right.

01:04:04.987 --> 01:04:06.887
Since there are three in a team,

01:04:07.017 --> 01:04:09.416
- one could feel left out.
- Yes.

01:04:09.417 --> 01:04:10.457
(Mind your actions, Yoon Hoo.)

01:04:11.287 --> 01:04:13.526
How much water should I add?

01:04:13.527 --> 01:04:14.596
(Starting with cooking rice)

01:04:14.597 --> 01:04:15.657
Let me see.

01:04:18.067 --> 01:04:19.927
- That much?
- This much?

01:04:20.297 --> 01:04:22.736
I haven't cooked rice in a long time.

01:04:22.737 --> 01:04:24.507
Do they have instant rice?

01:04:24.567 --> 01:04:25.737
We won't die.

01:04:26.967 --> 01:04:28.877
I have a feeling they'd have instant rice.

01:04:32.647 --> 01:04:35.247
- In here?
- There?

01:04:35.717 --> 01:04:37.647
Si Woo came next to him.

01:04:37.847 --> 01:04:39.317
Next to Hoo.

